          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve the City Planning BIN (Building Identification Number) associated with a set of account numbers. The procedure takes an XML input containing account numbers, processes this XML to extract the account numbers, and then performs a series of joins to fetch the corresponding City Planning BIN from the "
